@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nafiiv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(v1)
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.sin(tmp + 0.43) / v0))
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.21) * 0.88)
    v1 = wp.sin((0.22 * (tmp + 0.59 * v0 + 0.46)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
